title: Joe Kubert - Tor 1-6 (2008) (Minutemen)
description:
Joe Kubert's Tor 1-6 (2008) (Minutemen)

Written & illustrated by Joe Kubert
Published by DC.

Legendary writer/artist Joe Kubert returns to the gritty, primal world of Tor in this hardcover featuring the new six-issue miniseries adventure! Don't miss Tor's struggle for survival and his quest deep into a mysterious mountain where he will encounter strange tribes, primitive animals, destructive monsters and death at every turn.



This torrent contains:

Tor 001 (of 6) (2008) (ReEdit) (Minutemen-Zone & TheKid)
Tor 002 (of 6) (2008) (Minutemen-Y2K)
Tor 003 (of 6) (2008) (Minutemen-DT & TheKid)
Tor 004 (of 6) (2008) (Minutemen-DT & TheKid)
Tor 005 (of 6) (2008) (Minutemen-DT & TheKid)
Tor 006 (of 6) (2008) (Minutemen-DT & TheKid)
